@startuml
title Schedule Appointment State Diagram

[*] --> Unscheduled
Unscheduled --> Scheduled : order assigned date/time
Scheduled --> Rescheduled : customer changes date/time
Rescheduled --> Rescheduled : reschedule again
Scheduled --> Completed : delivered or picked up
Rescheduled --> Completed : delivered or picked up
Scheduled --> Cancelled : order cancelled
Rescheduled --> Cancelled : order cancelled
Completed --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]

@enduml
